'''''-issë''''' is a feminine agental suffix in [[Quenya]].
==Examples==
* ''mel'''issë''''' = "lover" (''mel-'' = "to love"; [[MEL]])<ref>{{HM|PM}}, p. 345</ref>
* ''[[Írissë]]''  = “Desirable Lady” (''írë'' = "desire")<ref>{{HM|PM}}, p. 345</ref>
==See also==
